1. While using netflix,we often see the recommendation movies, which is a valid application of AI
2.We also use face recognition for security reasons
3. The image recognition model that Facebook uses to identify the people in the image and give us tagging suggestions is also an example of AI.
4. Google Assistant, Apple Siri is an application of AI
5. Accurate google maps that has helped millions of people to avoid traffic and find their way is one of the most crucial examples of AI
